    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>For product / category pages there is a config option for this in the magento admin. But for normal CMS pages you need to add the following to the "design" tab on each page (obviouslyÂ change the URL to the correct one)</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
